New York Giants Defeat St. Louis Rams 28-16 to Raise Their Record to 1-1

-- B y   M i c h a e l   S i l l u p
-- 
2011-09-20T03:45:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/new-york-giants-defeat-st-louis-rams-28-16-to-raise-their-record-to-1-1.html
The  New York Giants  defeated the
St. Louis Rams 28-16 at MetLife Stadium in  East Rutherford ,  New
Jersey , to go 1-1 for the National Football League season. The
Rams fell to 0-2.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
